🚀 Security Camera Using Python & Webcam – Real-Time Motion Detection 🎥🔍
A low-cost surveillance system built with Python, OpenCV, and computer vision. This system transforms any webcam into a personal CCTV, detecting motion in real-time with image processing, frame differencing, contour detection, and instant audio alerts.

💡 Highlights:
✅ Real-time motion detection
✅ Cost-effective, customizable & efficient
✅ Technologies: Python, OpenCV

📌 Applications: Home security, office surveillance, and movement monitoring.
